Your Hosts

The voices behind the pod.

Andy Goode
England • Fly-Half • "Goodey"
18 years Pro, 482 professional games, 17 England caps, and one of the greatest Premiership operators. Goodey sees the game differently, straight-talking analysis, proper insight, and never afraid to call it as he sees it.
